  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Fish Tacos</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Fish Tacos</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meat</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">item</a> made in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by combining 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corn\" title=\"Corn\">Corn</a> and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\">Fishes</a>. It takes 10 seconds to cook.\n</p><p>Adding exactly 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twig</a> may result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a>, while adding 2 Twigs will result in Fish Tacos. Adding a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\">Mandrake</a> may result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a>.\n</p><p>Fish Tacos restores the same amount of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\">Hunger</a> as Fishsticks, but only half as much <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\">Health</a>. This dish is guaranteed not to gain any hunger over its components, and is more expensive than <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a> with only half the health value. It might be preferable to completely avoid this dish.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corn\" title=\"Corn\"><img alt=\"Corns.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corns.png?255bb9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes_Crock_Pot.png?7aa195\" width=\"525\" height=\"110\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>0.5</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corns\" title=\"Corns\"><img alt=\"Corns.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corns.png?255bb9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos\" title=\"Fish Tacos\"><img alt=\"Fish Tacos.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fish_Tacos.png?35050a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish\" title=\"Fish\"><img alt=\"Fish.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fish.png?e5d8f2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corn\" title=\"Corn\"><img alt=\"Corn.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corn.png?569259\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos\" title=\"Fish Tacos\"><img alt=\"Fish Tacos.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fish_Tacos.png?35050a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Prototype\" title=\"Prototype\"><img alt=\"Prototype.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Prototype.png/24px-Prototype.png?689878\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a> A recipe for getting the most hunger value.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corns\" title=\"Corns\"><img alt=\"Corns.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corns.png?255bb9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berry\" title=\"Berry\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos\" title=\"Fish Tacos\"><img alt=\"Fish Tacos.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fish_Tacos.png?35050a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>50% chance to make <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corns\" title=\"Corns\"><img alt=\"Corns.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corns.png?255bb9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Monster_Meats\" title=\"Monster Meats\"><img alt=\"Monster Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Monster_Meats.png?c5a3b6\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Durians\" title=\"Durians\"><img alt=\"Durians.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Durians.png?f5d732\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock P