 to make <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corns\" title=\"Corns\"><img alt=\"Corns.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corns.png?255bb9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos\" title=\"Fish Tacos\"><img alt=\"Fish Tacos.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fish_Tacos.png?35050a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td>33% chance to make <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a><br>33% chance to make <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake_Soup\" title=\"Mandrake Soup\">Mandrake Soup</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Corns\" title=\"Corns\"><img alt=\"Corns.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Corns.png?255bb9\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos\" title=\"Fish Tacos\"><img alt=\"Fish Tacos.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fish_Tacos.png?35050a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/64px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"64\" height=\"70\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Since Corn is required specifically, one can assume that Fish Tacos have <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corn_tortilla\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Corn tortilla\">corn tortillas</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:CD_fishtacos.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\"><img alt=\"Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don&#x27;t Starve.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/CD_fishtacos.png/120px-CD_fishtacos.png?d64940\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/CD_Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"CD Don&#x27;t Starve\">CD Don&#x27;t Starve</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Fish_Tacos_128x128.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\"><img alt=\"Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fish_Tacos_128x128.png/118px-Fish_Tacos_128x128.png?dbb445\" width=\"118\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fish_Tacos#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>  \n\n\n\n\n</div>",
