  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nFish Tacos\nFood Info\n37.5\n20\n5\nMeat\nObject Info\n6 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nCooking Info\nx0.5 x1 x2\n10 sec\n10\nMiscellaneous\n\"fishtacos\"\n“Crunchy and delicious!”\n–Wilson\n“Convenient taco-grip.”\n–Willow\n“Wolfgang hope is not too spicy.”\n–Wolfgang\n“I hope I got all the bones out.”\n–Wendy\n“THE FISH HAVE FULFILLED THEIR HIGHER PURPOSE”\n–WX-78\n“Oh, I do like a spot of spice on my fish.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“Tastes like the sea.”\n–Woodie\n“Cooked fish in a crunchy shell.”\n–Maxwell\n“Quite delicious concoction of fish and corn.”\n–Wagstaff\n“Fish in a blanket!”\n–Wigfrid\n“Taco Tuesday!”\n–Webber\n“All times are taco times.”\n–Walani\n“Takes me south of the border!”\n–Warly\n“Th'crunchy shell be delicious.”\n–Woodlegs\n“'TIS FISH AND BREAD”\n–Wilba\n“For belly”\n–Wormwood\n“Those dead fish heads look... appetizing?”\n–Wheeler\n“That's some good eating.”\n–Winona\n“More mortal food.”\n–Wortox\n“Fish not happy in there...”\n–Wurt\n“The s'more of fish dishes!”\n–Walter\n“I'll get a taco to go!”\n–Wanda\nFish Tacos is a Meat Food item made in the Crock Pot by combining 1 Corn and 1 Fishes. It takes 10 seconds to cook.\nAdding exactly 1 Twig may result in Fishsticks, while adding 2 Twigs will result in Fish Tacos. Adding a Mandrake may result in Mandrake Soup.\nFish Tacos restores the same amount of Hunger as Fishsticks, but only half as much Health. This dish is guaranteed not to gain any hunger over its components, and is more expensive than Fishsticks with only half the health value. It might be preferable to completely avoid this dish.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\n×0.5\n×2\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×2\nA recipe for getting the most hunger value.\n50% chance to make Fishsticks\n50% chance to make Monster Lasagna\n50% chance to make Mandrake Soup\n33% chance to make Fishsticks\n33% chance to make Mandrake Soup\n×2\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nSince Corn is required specifically, one can assume that Fish Tacos have corn tortillas.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nOriginal HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don't Starve.\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
