  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Tacos Cá là một Thực Phẩm Thịt được làm trong Nồi Hầm bằng cách kết hợp 1 Bắp và 1 Cá. Phải mất 10 giây để nấu ăn.</p>",
  "title": "Fish Tacos",
  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = {{FULLPAGENAME}}.png\n|image = {{FULLPAGENAME}} Dropped.png\n|foodType = [[Food_Type#Meat|Meat]] [[File:Meats.png|32px|link=Food_Type#Meat]]\n|foodRecipe = {{Pic|32px|Fishes}}x0.5 {{Pic|32px|Corns}}x1 {{Pic|32px|Filler}}x2\n|canBeBurned=1\n|spoil = 6 Days\n|stack = 40\n|hpRestored = 20\n|hungerRestored = 37.5\n|sanityRestored = 5\n|cooktime = 10 sec\n|priority = 10\n|crafting = Cooked in a [[Crock Pot]]\n|spawnCode = \"fishtacos\"\n}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Crunchy and delicious!\n|willow = Convenient taco-grip.\n|wolfgang = Wolfgang hope is not too spicy.\n|wendy = I hope I got all the bones out.\n|wx78 = THE FISH HAVE FULFILLED THEIR HIGHER PURPOSE\n|wickerbottom = Oh, I do like a spot of spice on my fish.\n|woodie = Tastes like the sea.\n|maxwell = Cooked fish in a crunchy shell.\n|wagstaff = Quite delicious concoction of fish and corn.\n|wigfrid = Fish in a blanket!\n|webber = Taco Tuesday!\n|walani = All times are taco times.\n|warly = Takes me south of the border!\n|woodlegs = Th'crunchy shell be delicious.\n|wilba = 'TIS FISH AND BREAD\n|wormwood = For belly\n|wheeler = Those dead fish heads look... appetizing?\n|winona = That's some good eating.\n|wortox = More mortal food.\n|wurt = Fish not happy in there...\n|walter = The s'more of fish dishes!\n|wanda = I'll get a taco to go!\n|choose = wurt\n}}\n'''Fish Tacos''' is a [[Meats|Meat]] [[Food]] [[item]] made in the [[Crock Pot]] by combining 1 [[Corn]] and 1 [[Fishes]]. It takes 10 seconds to cook.\n\nAdding exactly 1 [[Twigs|Twig]] may result in [[Fishsticks]], while adding 2 Twigs will result in Fish Tacos. Adding a [[Mandrake]] may result in [[Mandrake Soup]].\n\nFish Tacos restores the same amount of [[Hunger]] as Fishsticks, but only half as much [[Health]]. This dish is guaranteed not to gain any hunger over its components, and is more expensive than [[Fishsticks]] with only half the health value. It might be preferable to completely avoid this dish.\n\n== Prerequisites ==\n*Requires: [[File:Corns.png|link=Corn]]\n*Requires: [[File:Fishes Crock Pot.png|link=Fishes]]\n\n== {{pic|32|Cookbook}} Recipe ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|count1 = 0.5\n|item2 = Corns\n|item3 = Filler\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Fish Tacos\n}}\n\n== Examples ==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fish\n|item2 = Corn\n|item3 = Twigs\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Fish Tacos\n|note={{Pic24|Prototype}} A recipe for getting the most hunger value.}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|item2 = Corns\n|item3 = Twigs\n|item4 = Berry\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Fish Tacos\n|note = 50% chance to make [[Fishsticks]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|item2 = Corns\n|item3 = Monster Meats\n|item4 = Durians\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Fish Tacos\n|note = 50% chance to make [[Monster Lasagna]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|item2 = Corns\n|item3 = Morsels\n|item4 = Mandrake\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Fish Tacos\n|note = 50% chance to make [[Mandrake Soup]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|item2 = Corns\n|item3 = Twigs\n|item4 = Mandrake\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Fish Tacos\n|note = 33% chance to make [[Fishsticks]]<br/>33% chance to make [[Mandrake Soup]]\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Fishes\n|item2 = Corns\n|item3 = Ice\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Crock Pot\n|result = Fish Tacos\n|dlc = Reign of Giants\n}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* Since Corn is required specifically, one can assume that Fish Tacos have [[Wikipedia:Corn tortilla|corn tortillas]].\n== {{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nCD fishtacos.png|Original HD icon from Bonus Materials from [[CD Don't Starve]].\nFish Tacos 128x128.png|Icon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\n</gallery>\n\n{{Crock Pot Food}}\n__NOTOC__\n[[pl:Rybne takos]] [[fr:Tacos au poisson]] [[pt:Tacos de Peixe (Fish Tacos)]]\n[[Category:Crock Pot Recipes]]\n[[Category:Healing]]\n[[Category:Sanity Boost]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Perishables]]"
